\id TDX - Asang Khongca Bible (2019)
\mt1 Baibul pakrong zoihaih
\iot A
\p \k Aaeh:\k*
\li2 Mt. 14:19; 26:26; Lk 22:19; 1 Kr 11:24
\p \k Aah:\k*
\li2 athaih lak, thingthai qumpo lak, cang aah. Kami maeto mah a toksakhaih baktih toengah aat tih (Lp 14:14-20; 2 Kr 9:6-15; Kl 6:7-10; Mt 6:26; Kl 6:7)
\p \k Aanghaih:\k*
\li2 2 Th 2:8; Mt 5:14; 5:16; 11:30; Lk 2:32; Jn 1:4; 1:7; 1:9; 3:19; 8:12; 12:35; Tk 13:47; Ro 13:12; 2 Kr 6:14; Ef 5:8; 1 Th 5:5; 1 Jn 1:5; Lp 21:23
