\p \k Abomh:\k*
\li2 He 4:16
\p \k Abraham:\k*
\li2 Judah acaengnawk ih ampa. Tanghaih tangtang to Abraham khae hoi amtuk han angaih (Ro 4; He 11:8-19)
\p \k Acaeng:\k*
\li2 Mt 25; 32; 24:7; Tk 14:16; Fi 2:15; 1 Pi 2:9; Lp 5:9.
