\p \k Acoehaih paek:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:7; Tk 10:22; 1 Th 5:14; He 11:7
\p \k Acuu:\k*
\li2 Mt 23:37; Jn 4:36; Ef 1:10
\p \k Adam:\k*
\li2 Jesu loe acaeng boih amtong angthahaih ah oh pongah, Jesu kri loe Adam hoi patah ah oh. Jesu loe anih tang kaminawk khaeah hinghaih to paek. Ro 5:12-21; 1 Kr 15:20-22, 42-49
\p \k Aduesak, amcuksak (akaisak): \k*
\li2 Ro 12:2
