\p \k Akrang:\k*
\li2 Misong thung hoi akrang. Misong thung hoi loisak hanah atho paek. Jesu duekhaih rang hoiah aicae to zaehaih thung hoi akrang moe, loisak (Kl 3:10-14; Kl 4:1-7; Ef 1:7-8; Kol 1:13-14; He 2:11-15; 1 Ti 2:6; Mt 20:28)
\p \k Akunh:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:6; 18:8; 19:24; 25:21; Mk 14:38; Jn 3:4; 10:1; Ro 5:12; He 4:3
\p \k Aling:\k*
