\p \k Amtueng:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:16; Titu 2:11; 1 Jn 3:2
\p \k Amtuengsak:\k*
\li2 Kl 6:4
\p \k Amtuenghaih (angphonghaih): \k*
\li2 Kami maeto mah panoek ai ih hmuennawk patukhaih. Kami mah panoek ai ih hmuen patuek. Panoek ai ih hmuen hnuksakhaih (1Korin 2:6-16). Sithaw loe angmah ih kaminawk khaeah pathlonghaih, thacakhaih hoi amlunghaih to amtuengsak. Kawbaktih naah maw loe tahmaanawk hoi patoeh ih kaminawk khaeah amtueng pae (Rom 16:25-27; Efisa 3:2-5). Jesu long nuiah angzoh naah Sithaw mah aicae kawkruk maw palung, tito amtuengsak (Johan 1:1-18; Hebru 1:1-2)
\p \k Amtuenghaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:26; 11:25; Ro 1:17; 8:18; 16:25; Ef 1:17; 1 Th 2:3; Jn 7:24
\p \k Amtuk:\k*
\li2 Mt 11:29; He 5:8
\p \k Amuu (atii): Lk 8:11 \k*
\p \k Amzai:\k*
\li2 Lk 24:25; Ja 1:19
\p \k Angaih:\k*
\li2 Lk 12:20; 12:48; Mt 6:32; Lk 15:7; Ef 4:28; He 4:16; Lp 3:17
\p \k Angam duem:\k*
\li2 Lk 10:20; Ro 8:7; Ef 5:24; 1 Pi 2:18; 5:5
\p \k Angap (angpaek): Fi 3:21; Ef 5:21; Ja 4:7 \k*
\p \k angbawn:\k*
\li2 2 Ti 3:16
\p \k angbawhaih (hmuenpaekhaih): \k*
\li2 Zaehaih takhoe ving hanah Sithaw khaeah hmuenpaekhaih. Zaehaih thung hoi loih thai hanah Sithaw khae angbawnhaih. Sithaw khae tangqum paekhaih. Zae tahmen hanah Sithaw to hmuen hoiah bokhaih. Jesu loe aicae zaehaih pongah angmah ih takpum to aicae boih han vaito ah angpaek boeh (He 7:23-28; 9:23-28; Mt 9:13; Mk 9:49; Ef 5:2; Fi 4:18). Tangcaanawk loe Sithaw tok to sak o moe, Sithaw hmin pakoeh hanah vaihiah angmacae hoi angmacae to Sithaw khaeah, “kahing ah paek ih hmuen,” baktiah angpaek o (Ro 12:1-2; He 13:15-16)
\p \k Angcoeng thai ai:\k*
\li2 Mt 17:20; Lk 1:37; He 11:6
\p \k Angdaehhaih (raemhhaih): \k*
\li2 Misa ah kaom kami hnik salakah monghaih sak. Misa hoi misa angdaehsak let (Lk 12:57-59). Long kami loe zae pongah Sithaw hoi misa ah oh. Toe long kami hoi sithaw angdaehhaih sak hanah a Capa Jesu to patoeh (Ro 5:10-11; 2 Kr 5:16-21; Ef 2:11-18; Kol 1:19-23)
\p \k Angdoet:\k*
\li2 Mt 12:25; Lk 21:36; Ro 5:2; 2 Kr 1:24; Kl 5:1; Lp 3:20; Ja 5:9
\p \k Anghak:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 13:8; Kol 1:9; 1 Th 5:17
\p \k Anghmanghaih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 14:33
\p \k Anghmangsak:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 1:27
\p \k Anghmang thok:\k*
\li2 Panoek han rai parai hmuen. Sithaw mah thuih ih kathuk lok (Ro 16:25-27; Ef 3:1-13; Kol 1:24-29)
\p \k Anghmat:\k*
\li2 Mk 14:35; 1 Kr 7:31; Fi 4:7; 1 Jn 2:17, Jn 3:16; 1 Kr 8:11; 2 Pi 3:9; Mt 5:13; 10:42; 18:11; Lk 15:4; 19:10; 15:32
\p \k Anghmonghaih:\k*
\li2 Fi 2:7
\p \k Anghnai:\k*
\li2 Jn 6:44; Ja 4:8
\p \k Anghoe:\k*
\li2 He 11:25; Lk 1:44; 15:7; Jn 16:24; Ro 15:13; Kal 5:22; Fi 4:1; He 12:2; Ja 1:2; 1 Pi 4:13
\p \k Anghoehaih:\k*
\li2 Kl 6:4; He 3:6
\p \k Anghoe koi kaom:\k*
\li2 2 Kor 7:4
\p \k Anghuen:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:14; 11:7; He 12:27
\p \k Anghum tathuk:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:16; Mk 1:10; Jn 1:32; 1 Th 4:16
\p \k Angkhaeh (amro): \k*
\li2 Mt 21:44
\p \k Angkhukhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 7:15; Mk 12:38
\p \k Angkhuksak:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:30; 25:36; 1 Pi 5:5
\p \k Angkomhaih:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 6:14; 13:14; Tk 2:42; 1 Kr 1:9; 2 Kr 8:4; Ef 5:11; Fi 1:5; 3:10; 1 Jn 1:6
\p \k Angkrihaih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 15:33; Ef 4:29; Kol 3:8
\p \k Angmah ih:\k*
\li2 Jn 1:11; 1 Kr 6:19
\p \k Angoephaih:\k*
\li2 Ef 3:12; Fi 3:3
\p \k Angphak:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:33; 16:24; 26:34; 2 Ti 2:12
\p \k Angpaek:\k*
\li2 Ro 8:38; 12:1; 1 Kr 5:3; 2 Kr 5:8; Kol 1:22
\p \k Angpaekhaih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 9:27; 1 Pi 3:5
\p \k Angpaek (hmuenpaek): \k*
\li2 1 Kr 5:7; 1 Pi 2:5
\p \k Angpaekhaih:\k*
\li2 Zaehaih tahmat hanhoi zae tahmen hanah angpaekhaih. Jesu loe hae long nuiah angzoh moe, angmah ih kaminawk zaehaih pongah a hinghaih to paek (Ro 3:21-26; He 10:1-18)
\p \k Angqai:\k*
\li2 Mt 24:12; Lp 3:15
\p \k Angqoi:\k*
\li2 Mt 18:3; Lk 22:32
\p \k Angraeng:\k*
\li2 Mt 19:23; Lk 1:53; 6:24; 16:1; 18:23; 2 Kr 6:10; 8:9; Ef 2:4; 1 Ti 6:18; Ja 2:5
\p \k Angraenghaihnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 13:22; 2 Kr 8:2; Ef 1:7; 2:7; Kol 1:27
\p \k Angraeng hoi kasaeng:\k*
\li2 Ja 2:8; 1 Pi 2:9
\p \k Angraeng:\k*
\li2 Baibul thung ih A kathoeng loe long angraeng, kami ukkung hoi akaa tawn kami thuihhaihih ni. Toe A kalen loe Sithaw thuih koehhaih ih ni (Mt 11:25; Ro 10:9-13; 1 Kr 12:3; Fi 2:9-11)
\p \k Angraeng buh:\k*
\li2 Jesu mah a hnukbangnawk hoi caak ih buh (Mt 26:17-30; Lk 22:7-30). Jesu anghum let naah nihcae hoi nawnto buhcaa let tih (Jn 6:25-59; 1 Kr 10:14-17; 1 Kr 11:17-34; Lp 19:9; Tk 20:7)
\p \k Angraeng:\k*
\li2 Mk 2:28; Ro 14:9; 16:12; Ef 4:5; 1 Ti 6:15; Lp 14:13; 17:14
\p \k Angraeng ni:\k*
\li2 Cabu kaciim thungah Sithaw mah angzo hankoi atue ah kahoih ai hmuen paro han ih atue thuih naah patoh (2Pi 3:1-13)
\p \k angraeng:\k*
\li2 Jn 12:31; Tk 3:15; Ef 2:2
\p \k angraengnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 20:25; 1 Kr 2:6
\p \k Angraeng tangkhang:\k*
\li2 He 4:16; Lp 22:3
\p \k Angsakhaih:\k*
\li2 Kl 5:20; 2 Piter 5:1
\p \k Angthasak let:\k*
\li2 Ro 12:2; 2 Kr 4:16; Ef 4:23; Titu 3:5
\p \k Angthawk:\k*
\li2 1 Th 4:16
\p \k Angthawk lethaih:\k*
\li2 Duek pacoeng hing lethaih. Duekhaih thung hoi angthawk lethaih. Zae pongah duekhaih long nuiah angzoh (Lk 7:11-17; 20:36; Jn 5:29; 11:25; He 11:35; Lp 20:5). Jesu angthawk lethaih mah duekhaih to pazawk (Mt 28; Lk 24; Tk 2:22-39). Jesu duekhaih thung hoi angthawk let baktih toengah tangcaanawk doeh Jesu anghum let naah loe taksa kangtha hoi angthawk o let tih (Ro 6:1-10; 1 Kr 15; Fi 3:7-21). Hnukkhuem koek angthawk lethaih niah loe dueh kaminawk boih Sithaw mah lokcaek hanah duekhaih thung hoi angthawk o let tih (Mt 22:23-33; Lp 20:11-15)
\p \k Angthawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 11:5; Lk 1:69; Ro 4:25; 6:4; 2 Kr 4:14; Ef 5:14
\p \k Angthla:\k*
\li2 Mk 12:34; Ef 2:13
\p \k Angthuih:\k*
\li2 Tk 17:28; He 12:28; 2 Pi 1:21
\p \k Angvan:\k*
\li2 Lk 2:36; Jn 5:18; Fi 2:6
\p \k Angvin:\k*
\li2 Kalah prae kami, hnuk vai ai ih kami (Mt 25:35; Ef 2:19; He 13:2; 1 Pi 2:11)
\p \k Angvin khetzawnhaih:\k*
\li2 Rm 12:13; Titu 1:8; 1 Pi 4:9
\p \k Angzoh:\k*
\li2 Mt 20:28; Jn 1:11; Mt 3:11; 11:28; 16:24; Lk 14:20; Jn 6:35; 6:44; 7:37; 14:18; 1 Kr 11:26; He 4:16; Lp 22:17
\p \k Angzohhaih:\k*
\li2 2 Pi 3:12
\p \k Ani:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:34; 1 Kr 1:8; 2 Pi 1:19
\p \k Aninawk:\k*
\li2 Ef 5:16; 2 Pi 3:3
\p \k Ap (paek): Jn 10:22 \k*
\p \k Aphum:\k*
\li2 Mt 8:21; Ro 6:4; Kol 2:12
\p \k Aqum:\k*
\li2 Lk 12:20; Jn 3:2; 9:4; 11:10; Ro 13:12; Lp 21:25
\p \k Athaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 7:17; 26:29; Lk 1:42; Kl 5:22; Ef 5:9; He 12:11
\p \k Athaih athaih:\k*
\li2 Jn 15:2; 15:8; Kol 13:7; Lk 13:9; Kl 6:2; He 9:28
\p \k Athaih tangsuek:\k*
\li2 Kathai hmaloe thingthai qumpo. Kathai hmaloe thingthai qumpo to lak moe, Sithaw khae paekhaih (Ro 8:23-25; 1 Kr 15:20-23). Poihsakhaih, caaknaek poihsakhaih (Lk 14:15-24; 22:14-19)
\p \k Athaih tangsuek:\k*
\li2 Ro 8:23; 1 Kr 15:20; Ja 1:18
\p \k Athi:\k*
\li2 Baibul thungah loe hinghaih thuih koehhaih ih ni. Angpaekhaih athii loe atho oh (Ro 5:9-11; He 9:11-28; Lp 5:9-10)
\p \k Athi:\k*
\li2 Mt 26:28; 27:8; Lk 22:44; Jn 1:13; 6:54; Ro 3:25; 1 Kr 11:27; Ef 1:7; He 12:24; 1 Pi 1:19; 1 Jn 1:7
\p \k Athi long:\k*
\li2 Mt 26:28
\p \k Atho:\k*
\li2 Mt 13:46; 1 Kr 6:20
\p \k Atho paek:\k*
\li2 Loih thai hanah hmuen paekhaih. Kami maeto sakpazaehaih thung hoi loih thai hanah hmuen paek moe loisak. Jesu loe angmah ih kaminawk zae misong thung hoi loisak hanah angmah hoi angmah to angpaek (Mak 10:45; He 9:15)
\p \k Atho kaom:\k*
\li2 Ef 3:7; Ja 5:16; 1 Pi 1:19; 2:4; 1 Ti 4:8; 2 Ti 3:16
\p \k Atho oh:\k*
\li2 Mt 15:6; 1 Kr 1:17; Kl 5:4
\p \k Atho oh (amek): 1 Kr 13:3 \k*
\p \k Athum:\k*
\li2 Jn 21:25; 1 Kr 7:9
\p \k Athung:\k*
\li2 Mt 7:15; Ro 2:29; 2 Kr 4:16
\p \k Atoengh (paloep tahang): \k*
\li2 Mt 23:12; Lk 1:52; Fi 2:9
\p \k Atoengh tahang:\k*
\li2 Jn 3:14; 8:28; 12:32; 1 Ti 2:8; Ja 4:10
\p \k Atue:\k*
\li2 Lk 19:44; 2 Kr 6:2; Ef 5:16; Jn 5:35; Tk 1:7; 2 Ti 4:2; Kol 4:6; Mt 24:36; 25:13; Lk 12:12; Jn 2:4
\p \k Atuen:\k*
\li2 1 Ti 1:10; 1 Ti 1:7
\p \k Atuenawk:\k*
\li2 Tk 1:7; Ef 2:11-22
\p \k Atue phak:\k*
\li2 Mt 24:45; Lk 12:42; Ro 13:7; Kl 6:9
\p \k Azaem:\k*
\li2 Lk 12:33; 22:32; 1 Kr 13:8; 1 Pi 1:4; 5:4
\p \k Azat:\k*
\li2 Tk 5:41; He 12:2
\p \k Azat paek:\k*
\li2 Ja 2:1
\p \k Azat paekhaih:\k*
\li2 Ef 5:33; He 12:28
\p \k Azit:\k*
\li2 Mt 11:28
\p \k Azom ah:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:8; Ro 3:24; 8:32
\p \k Azompui:\k*
\li2 Ro 1:21; 2 Kr 6:1; Ef 5:6
\iot B
\p \k Babilon:\k*
\li2 Babilon kaminawk ih vangpui. Babilon kaminawk mah Jerusalem to praek o moe, paroeai kaminawk to misong ah hoih o. Baibul hnukkhuem koek ah Babilon loe Sithaw lok aek taqawk thacakhaih angmathaih maeto ah amtueng (Lp 17-18)
\p \k Ban:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:30; 6:3; 2:21; 25:33; Mk 14:62; Tk 2:33; Ro 8:34; Kol 3:1; 1 Pi 3:22
\p \k Bannawk:\k*
\li2 Lk 23:46; Jn 13:3; Ef 4:28; 1 Ti 2:8; He 10:31
\p \k Bangkraih:\k*
\li2 Mt 25:36; 1 Kr 4:11; 2 Kr 5:3; Lp 16:15
\p \k Bangh:\k*
\li2 Mt 18:6; 22:40
\p \k Ban payangh:\k*
\li2 Mt 12:13
\p \k Banpayung:\k*
\li2 Jn 20:27
\p \k Bet:\k*
\li2 Lp 3:15
\p \k Boeng (takroek): \k*
\li2 Mt 5:30; 18:8
\p \k Boengloeng:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:42; 20:22; 26:39; 1 Kr 10:16; 11:25
\p \k Boeng:\k*
\li2 Tk 13:47; Mt 13:39; 24:13; 28:20; Jn 13:1; Ro 6:21; 1 Kr 1:8; He 3:14; 1 Pi 4:7; Lp 1:8; 21:6
\p \k Boh:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:39
\p \k Boihboih:\k*
\li2 1 Th 5:23; 1 Ti 4:15
\p \k Bokhaih:\k*
\li2 Ja 1:27
\p \k Bokhaih:\k*
\li2 “Lu takhum,” tiah thuih koehaih ih ni. Bokhaih loe Sithaw khingyahaih kasang koek ni. Cabu kaciim mah Sithaw loe bok han krak, tiah thuih. Kaminawk ih palungthin loe Sithaw tangtang bok ai ah kalah hmuennawk to bok o lat (Mt 4:8-10; Ro 1:25; 12:1-2; Lp 5:14; 22:9; 14:6-12; 7:9-17; Tk 17:23; Jn 4:23-24)
\p \k Bomkung:\k*
\li2 3 Jn 1:8
\p \k Buhcaakhaih:\k*
\li2 Lk 14:16; Lp 19:9
\p \k Buhzah:\k*
\li2 Mt 4:2; 6:16
\p \k Buhzahhaih:\k*
\li2 Buhcaa ai ah ohhaih. Buhzah lawkthuihaih (Tk 13:1-3; Lk 2:37; 2 Kr 6:5)
\iot C
\p \k Ca tarikkung (daan patukkung): \k*
\li2 Kaalok sah kami, ukhaih daan sah kami. Ca tarik kop kami. Jesu dung nathuem ah kaom ca tarik kaminawk loe long nui zehoihaih daan (upadi) kop kami ah oh o. Nihcae loe Judah phung patukhaih hoi Mosi mah paek ih kaalok kop parai kami ah oh o (1Kr 14:33; He 12:2; Mt 8:18-20; 15:1-20; Mk 1:21-22; 12:28-40; Lk 5:17-32; 19:45-48; 23:8-11)
\p \k Cabi:\k*
\li2 Mt 16:19; Lp 1:18
\p \k Caboi:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 10:21
\p \k Cabu:\k*
\li2 Jn 21:25; Fi 4:3; Lp 20:15
\p \k Cabuciim:\k*
\li2 Mt 22:29; Tk 17:11; Ro 15:4; 2 Ti 3:15-16
\p \k Caanawk (adung kaminawk): \k*
\li2 Mt 3:7; Kol 1:26; 1 Pi 2:9
\p \k Caeh tahang:\k*
\li2 Jn 20:17
\p \k Caeh taak (tacawt taak): \k*
\li2 Mt 19:5; Ro 12:9; Mt 7:23; 25:41; Lk 2:29; Fi 1:23; Mt 19:27; 27:46; 2 Kr 4:9; He 13:5
\p \k Caehtaak:\k*
\li2 Mt 19:5; Mk 10:7; Jn 14:18; 14:27; Ef 5:31; He 13:5
\p \k Caehtaak ving:\k*
\li2 Mt 26:21; Mk 13:12; 14:18; Jn 13:21
\p \k Caek:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 11:28; 2 Kr 13:5
\p \k Caak (paro): \k*
\li2 Mt 23:14; Kl 5:15; 1 Pi 5:8
