\li2 Ef 3:15
\p \k Cang:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:12; Lk 22:31; Jn 12:24
\p \k Cang aah:\k*
\li2 Mt 9:3; Lp 14:15
\p \k Capa:\k*
\li2 Mt 4:3; 11:27; 16:16; Jn 1:18; 3:16; 8:36; Ro 8:32; 1 Kr 1:9
\p \k capanawk:\k*
\li2 He 2:10; 12:7; 1 Jn 3:1
\p \k Capat:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 3:2; 2 Th 2:15
\p \k Cawnh:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:7; 1 Kr 6:18; Ja 4:7; Kl 2:2; He 12:1
\p \k Cawnhaih ahmuen:\k*
\li2 Tk 20:24; 2 Ti 4:7
\p \k Cawn angnoekhaih:\k*
\li2 He 12:1
\p \k Ciimcai:\k*
\li2 Ro 7:12; 12:1; Ef 2:21;1Pi 2:5; 2:9; Lp 4:8
\p \k Ciimcaihaih:\k*
\li2 Ro 1:4; 2 Kr 7:1; Ef 4:24; 1 Ti 2:15; He 12:10
\p \k Ciimcaihaih: Ciimcaisak; thoengsak:\k*
\li2 Sithaw mah patoh hanah suek. Jesu mah aicae han angpaekhaih rang hoiah a hnukbang kaminawk to ciimcaisak (1Kr 6:9-11; He 10:10). Sithaw ih kaminawk ciimcai ah hing thai hanah Kacai Muithla mah abomh (Jn 17:15-19; 1 Th 4:3-8; 2 Th 2:13-15; He 12:14)
\p \k Ciimcai ai:\k*
\li2 Kamhnong; kakhoem ngang. Thoengkai ai. Canghnii dung ah ciimcai ai kami loe Sithaw bokhaih imthung ah akun thai ai. Ciimcai ai kami hoi hmuen loe ciimcai hmaloe han angaih. Ciimcai ai tihhaih loe Muithla bang ciimcai ai thuih koehhaih ih ni. Jesu rang hoiah tangcaanawk loe ciimcaisak boeh (Mk 7:1-23; Tk 10; Ro 14:13-18; 14:14)
\p \k Ciimcaisak (thoengsak): \k*
\li2 Mt 23:25; Jn 17:17; 1 Th 5:23
\p \k Ciimsak (thoengsak): \k*
\li2 Mt 10:8; Lk 17:17; Ef 5:26; 1 Jn 1:7; Titu 2:14; Ja 4:8
\p \k Cingceng:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 13:1
\p \k Coekkoi om ai:\k*
\li2 Lk 1:6; 1 Th 5:23; 2 Pi 3:14
\p \k Coekkoi kaom:\k*
\li2 He 9:14; 1 Pi 1:19; 2 Pi 3:14
\p \k Cungh (thingboeng): Lp 12:5 \k*
\iot D
\p \k Daan:\k*
\li2 Sitawh ih Kaalok congca oh. Sithaw ih Kaalok cabu (Tk 13:39; Ro 2:12; 7:12; 1 Kr 6:7; Kl 2:19; 3:10; 5:23; Fi 3:9; He 7:19; Ja 1:25
\p \k Daan congca:\k*
\li2 Kl 6:16; Fi 3:16; Kol 3:15; 1 Ti 3:5, Mt 5:17-20; Ro 7:1, 8:17; Kl 3:15-25; Fi 3:7-11; Ro 13:8-10; Kl 5:13-15; Jn 13:34-35; Ja 1:19-25; Ro 3:21
\p \k Daan (upadi) ai ah nongpa nongpata zae sakhaih:\k*
\li2 Ef 5:5; He 13:4; Lp 21:8; 17:1
\p \k Daan ai ah zaehaih sah kami:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 5:9; He 12:16
\p \k Daan ai ah zaesakhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 15:19; Jn 8:41; 1 Kr 5:1; 10:8; Kl 5:19; 1 Th 4:3; Lp 14:8; 17:4
\p \k Daanpaek:\k*
\li2 2 Th 1:9
\p \k Dantui:\k*
\li2 Mt 28:3; Lp 1:14
\p \k Dawncang ai:\k*
\li2 1 Ti 4:14; He 2:3
\p \k Dawnpakhuem:\k*
\li2 Zaehaih thung hoi angqoi moe, Sithaw loklam pazuihaih. Dawnpakhuem tih haih ih loe kami maeto khosakhaih dan hoi a hinghaih dan amkhraihaih ih ni (Mk 1:15; Lk 13:3; Tk 2:38; Lp 2:16
\p \k Dawnpakhuemhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:11; 9:13; Mk 1:4; Lk 15:7; 24:47; Ro 2:4; 2 Kr 7:10; 2 Pi 3:9; Tk 20:21
\p \k Dawnrai:\k*
\li2 Sithaw thacakhaih rang hoiah sak ih kalen dawnrai hmuen (Lk 7:11-17; Jn 10:22-42; Tk 2:22; He 2:22; 2 Th 2:9-12; Lp 13:11-17; Lk 4:22)
\p \k Dawnrai hmuen:\k*
\li2 Mk 9:39; Tk 2:22; 1 Kr 12: 10; Kl 3:5
\p \k Dawnrainawk:\k*
\li2 Jn 4:48; Lp 13:13
\p \k David: \k*
\li2 Lensawk Israel siangpahrang. Jesu loe David ih imthung takoh thung hoiah tacawt. Anih loe Sithaw ih prae dungzan ah uk hankoi David ih capa ah oh (Lk 1:31-33; Tk 2:22-36; Ro 1:1-4)
\p \k Dueh thai ai:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 15:53; 2 Ti 1:10
\p \k Dueh thaih koi:\k*
\li2 Ro 6:12; 1 Kr 15:53
\p \k Duek:\k*
\li2 Ro 5:8; 1 Kr 15:3; Mt 26:35; Jn 8:21; 11:50; Ro 14:8; Fi 1:21; Mt 8:22; Lk 8:52; Jn 11:25; Ro 6:8; Kl 2:19; Ef 2:1; 1 Th 4:16; 2 Ti 2:11; Lp 14:13
\p \k Duekhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 16:28; Jn 5:24; Ro 5:12; 8:2; 8:38; 1 Kr 11:26; 15:54; 2 Kr 4:12; Fi 2:8; He 2:9; 1 Jn 3:14; Lp 21:4
\p \k Duemh:\k*
\li2 Ro 3:23
\p \k Dungzan:\k*
\li2 Boenghaih kaom ai, kaboeng thai ai. Sithaw loe dungzan ah hing. Jesu hnukbangnawk loe dungzan hinghaih tangqum to paek (Jn 6:66-69; 10:10; 27-28; 2 Kr 4:16-18)
\p \k Dungzan:\k*
\li2 Mt 19:16; Mk 3:29; 10:17; Lk 10:25; Jn 3:15; 6:54; 17:3; Tk 13:48; Ro 2:7; 6:23; 2 Kr 4:17; 1 Ti 1:17; Titu 3:7; He 5:9; 1 Pi 5:10; 1 Jn 5:11
\iot F
\p \k Farasi:\k*
\li2 Kalahta ah oh, to tih ai boeh loe kamhoe ah oh, tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni. Farasinawk loe Cabu kangtha thung ah Judahnawk bokhaih bang lokpui koek zaehoikung ah oh o. Nihcae loe Cabu kangquem pazui kaminawk ni. Angmacae mah sak ih daan doeh cabu kaciim thungah khrumh o. To pongah vaihi hoi vaihi Jesu hoi lok angaekhaih to oh (Mt 23; Mk 7:1-23; Lk 18:9-14; Tk 26:4-5
\iot G
\p \k Gentelnawk:\k*
\li2 Gentel loe “acaengnawk,” tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni. Judah kami na ai, kalah acaeng kaminawk boih to Gentel, tiah kawk o (Tk 10:1-48; Ro 15:7-13; Ef 2:11-3:6; Lp 5:9-10
\p \k Gentelnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:32; Lk 2:32; Tk 13:47; Ro 11:25; Ef 3:6
\iot H
\p \k Haeh:\k*
\li2 Mt 13:3; Lk 12:24; 19:22; 1 Kr 15:42; 2 Kr 9:6; Kl 6:7
\p \k Hak (hnuk): Mt 16:26; Fi 1:21 \k*
\p \k Halleluia:\k*
\li2 Sithaw saphaw, tih haih ih ni. Hebru lokmu kangbok hnetto patoh hmaek ih lok ah oh. “Hallelu” loe (saphaw, pakoeh,) tiah thuih koehhaih ah oh moe, “Yah” loe (Sithaw ih ahmin hanah) “Yahweh” to tih ai boeh loe “Angraeng,” tih haih ih ni (Lp 19:1-8)
\p \k Haato thungah maeto:\k*
\li2 Haato 1/10 tih haih ih ni. Cabu kangquem ah Sithaw kaminawk loe angmacae ih lawk hoi tacawt thingthai qumponawk haato thungah maeto Sithaw hanah paek o. Thuih koehhaih loe Sithaw loe long tawnkung ah oh moe, anih mah angmah ih kaminawk to tahamhoihaih paek, tiah amtuengsakhaih ih ni. To tiah paek ih hmuen to qaima (pastor) hoi Levinawk, pacoengah kamtang kamlai kaminawk abomhhaih hanah patoh o (He 7:4-14).
\p \k Hawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 11:25; 1 Kr 4:5; 2 Kr 4:3; Kol 2:3; 3:3
\p \k Hell:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:22; 10:28; 16:18; Mk 9:45; Lk 12:5; Tk 2:27; Ja 3:6; Lp 1:18
\p \k Hell (Taqawk khaw): \k*
\li2 Kadueh kaminawk ih ahmuen (Mt 16:13-20; Lp 1:12-18; 19:1-8)
\p \k Hingh:\k*
\li2 Hb 7:25; Lp 1:18; Mt 4:4; Tk 17:28; Ro 8:13; 14:8; 2 Kr 13:11; Kl 2:20; 5:25; Fi 1:21
\p \k Hinghaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:25; 10:39: 20:28; Jn 1:4; 3:36; 5:40; 6:35; 8:12; 10:10; 11:25; 14:6: Ro 5:17; 2 Kr 2:16; 3:6; Kol 3:3; 1 Jn 5:12
\p \k Hoih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 6:12
\p \k Hoihhaih:\k*
\li2 Ro 2:4; Kl 5:22; Ef 5:9; 1 Kr 2:1; Fi 3:8
\p \k Hoikue:\k*
\li2 Fi 1:23; 2:3; He 8:6; 11:16; 11:35
\p \k Homh:\k*
\li2 1 Ti 3:15
\p \k Hmai:\k*
\li2 Mk 9:43; Lk 3:17; He 12:29
\p \k Hmaicam:\k*
\li2 Sithaw khaeah hmuen paekhaih ahmuen. Sithaw khaeah tangqum paekhaih ahmuen. Thoemto prae ah loe sum, thlung, thing hoiah sak ih hmaicam doeh oh (Lp 8:1-5; Mt 5:23; Tk 17:23; He 13:10; Lp 9:13)
\p \k Hmaidan:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 13:12; 2 Kr 3:18; Ja 1:23
\p \k Hmaiim:\k*
\li2 Mt 25:1; Lp 4:5
\p \k Hmaloe:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:33; 19:30; Tk 26:23; 1 Jn 4:19
\p \k Hmaipalai:\k*
\li2 Mt 13:50
\p \k Hmaithawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:15; Lk 15:8; Lp 1:20
\p \k Hmai kangh:\k*
\li2 Lk 3:17; 24:32; 1 Kr 7:9; 13:3; Lp 21:8
\p \k Hmai paanghaih ahmuen:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:15; Lk 11:33
\p \k Hmuenmae:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 10:24; Mt 6:19; 6:21; 13:52; 19:21; Lk 12:21; 2 Kr 4:7; Ro 6:13
\p \k Hmuen kazit:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 4:17; He 12:1; Mt 11:30; 23:4; Kl 6:2
\p \k Hmuenpaekhaih:\k*
\li2 Sithaw khae hmuen paekhaih. Cabu kangquem thungah loe Sithaw khaeah caaknaek hoi moinawk to paek o (Mk 12:28-34). Jesu loe hmuen tathlanghaih baktiah angmah hoi angmah to Sithaw khaeah angpaek (Ef 5:1-2; He 10:1-18; 1 Pi 2:4-5)
\p \k Hmuenpaekhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 6:1; Lk 12:33; Efi 5:2; He 10:14
\p \k Hmuen zawhhaih tok:\k*
\li2 Lk 2:49; Ro 12:11
\p \k Hmuihoih:\k*
\li2 Sithaw hmaa ah thlaek ih hmuihoih (Mt 2:7-12; Lp 8:1-5)
\p \k Hmuihoih tui:\k*
\li2 Mt 26:12; Lk 7:37; Jn 12:5
\p \k Hnam (hmuen phawhhaih): \k*
\li2 Mt 11:29; 2 Kr 6:14; Kl 5:1
\p \k Hnik:\k*
\li2 Lk 16:3; Mt 7:7; 20:22; Jn 14:14; Ef 3:20; Ja 4:2; 1 Jn 3:22; Fi 4:6
\p \k Hnuk:\k*
\li2 Mt 7:7; 10:39; 11:29; Lk 11:10; He 4:16
\p \k Hnuk (khet): \k*
\li2 Mt 6:1; Jn 1:18; 12:45; 20:29; 1 Ti 6:16; He 11:1; 1 Jn 3:2; Lp 22:4
\p \k Hnuk (hak): \k*
\li2 Mt 7:8; 10:8; 10:40; Jn 1:11; Tk 17:11; Ro 8:15; 15:7; He 11:13; 1 Kr 9:24; Ef 1:11; He 6:15
\p \k Hnukhaih:\k*
\li2 Amang baktiah hnukhaih. Sithaw mah kami khaeah tamthang sinsak han paek ih hmuen hnuksakhaih (Tk 10:1-23; 2 Kr 5:7)
\p \k Hnukung:\k*
\li2 Lk 1:2; 2 Pi 1:16; Jn 5:37; Tk 14:17; 1 Jn 5:10; Lp 1:5
\p \k Hnukungnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 18:16; 2 Kr 13:1; 1 Ti 6:12; 12:1
\p \k Hnukbang:\k*
\li2 Minawk hnukbang kami. Zaehoikung mah patuk ih baktih toengah sah kami. Jesu hnukbang kami hathlai hnetto oh. Toe vaihniah loe mi kawbaktih doeh Jesu to tang moe, anih patukhaih baktiah sah kami loe anih hnukbang kami ah oh (Mt 28:16-20; Lk 6:12-16; 14:25-35; Jn 15:1-17)
\p \k Hnukbanghaih:\k*
\li2 Ro 1:5; 1 Kr 9:2
\p \k Hnukbangnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:2; Lk 11:49; 1 Kr 15:9; Ef 2:20; Mt 1:24; Jn 8:31
\p \k Hnuk han krak:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:10; Lk 3:8; 10:7; 15:19; Tk 5:41; Ro 8:18; Ef 4:1; 1 Th 2:12; 1 Ti 1:15; 5:18; He 3:3; Lp 5:12
\p \k Hnukma:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:22; Lk 19:14; Jn 12:25; Ro 9:13; Ef 5:29; 1 Jn 2:9; Lk 14:26; Ro 7:15
\p \k Hnuk thaikoi ah oh:\k*
\li2 Kl 5:6; Ja 5:16
\p \k Hnuk thai ai:\k*
\li2 Kol 1:16; 1 Ti 1:17
\p \k Hrang:\k*
\li2 Lp 6:8
\p \k Hum (paduek): \k*
\li2 Mt 10:28; Jn 16:2; 2 Kr 3:6
\iot I
\p \k Ih (iih angmuet): 1 Kr 15:6; 1 Th 4:13 \k*
\p \k Ihhaih:\k*
\li2 Ro 13:11; 1 Kr 15:51
\p \k Im:\k*
\li2 Mt 10:13; 12:25; Lk 11:17; Jn 4:53; 14:2
\p \k Tk 16:31; 1 Pi 4:17; 2 Kr 5:6 \k*
\p \k Imnawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 23:14; Mk 10:29
\p \k Imtaeng:\k*
\li2 Mt 19:19; 22:39; Lk 10:29
\p \k Imsahkung:\k*
\li2 Mt 21:42; Mk 12:10; He 11:10; 1 Pi 2:7
\p \k Im pakaahaih kahni:\k*
\li2 Mt 27:51; He 6:19
\p \k Imthung takoh kami:\k*
\li2 Tk 16:15; Kl 6:10
\p \k Israel:\k*
\li2 Thuih koehhaih ih loe, anih loe Sithaw hoi angpan, to tih ai boeh loe thapathok tih haih ih ni. Van kami hoi angpan pacoengah Jakob han paek ih ahmin ah oh. Israelnawk loe Jakob khae hoi tacawt acaeng ah oh o (Ro 9-11)
\iot J
\p \k Jako:\k*
\li2 Isak capa. Jakob loe Israel acaeng hathlai hnettonawk ih ampa ah oh (He 11:20-21)
\p \k Jerusalem:\k*
\li2 Israel prae thungah lokpui koek vangpui. Jesu mah Jerusalem qahhaih (He 12:22; Lk 13:31-35; 19:28-44; Lp 21:2; 22:26)
\p \k Jesu:\k*
\li2 Grik hmin “Pathlongkung,” tih haih ih ni. Hebru lok hoi loe “Joshua,” “Angraeng mah pathlong,” tih haih ih ni (Mt 1; Lk 1:26-38). Jesu loe thumto kangkom Sithaw ah oh (Jn 1:1-18; Fi 2:1-11; Kol 1:15-20). Jesu loe kami tangtang ah oh (He 2:10-18; 4:14-15)
\p \k Judah:\k*
\li2 Judah acaeng thung hoi kanghum kami ih ahmin. Hnukkhuem ah loe Jakob (Israel) imthung takohnawk boih thuih hanah patoh (Ro 10:11-13; Kl 3:26-29)
\p \k Judah (Judahnawk): \k*
\li2 Ro 2:10; 1 Kr 9:20; Kl 3:28
\iot K
\p \k Kaalok:\k*
\li2 Kaminawk lok tahngaih han patuk ih Sithaw ih kaalok, to tih ai boeh loe daan. Kahoihah khosak thai hanah Sithaw mah angmah ih kaminawk khaeah kaalok to paek (Mt 22:34-40)
\p \k Kaalok:\k*
\li2 Mt 22:38; Jn 13:34; 15:12; 1 Ti 1:5; 1 Jn 3:23
\p \k Kaaloknawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 22:40; Mk 10:19; 1 Jn 3:24
\p \k Kacai:\k*
\li2 Sithaw han pahoehaih. Sithaw han paekhaih. Kaciim ah ohhaih (Ro 12:1-2; 1 Pi 1:13-16)
\p \k Kacai Muithla:\k*
\li2 Toksak naah thumto ah kangkom Sithaw thungah maeto. Kacai Muithla toksakhaih rang hoiah kaciim cabu sakthaih (2Pi 1:19-21). Kacai Muithla loe tangcaanawk khaeah oh moe, loihhaih hoi hinghaih kangtha to paek (Jn 14:15-31; Tk 2:1-21; Ro 8:1-27; 1 Kr 2:6-16; Kl 5:16-26)
\p \k Kacai Muithla:\k*
\li2 Lk 11:13; Ef 1:13; 4:30; Mt 1:18; 3:11; Mk 13:11; Lk 1:15; 3:22; 12:12; Jn 7:39; 14:26; Tk 1:8; 2:38; 7:51; 10:44; 15:28; Ro 5:5; 14:17; 1 Kr 13:14; Titu 3:5; 2 Pi 1:21; 1 Jn 5:7; Jd 1:20
\p \k Kacoehta:\k*
\li2 Tk 14:23; Titu 1:5; Ja 5:14; 1 Pi 5:5; Lp 4:4
\p \k Kacoehtanawk:\k*
\li2 Saning coeh kaminawk. Kricaabu zaehoikung kacoehtanawk (Fi 1:1; 1 Ti 3:8)
\p \k Kacuem (cuemhaih): 2 Kr 11:2 \k*
\p \k Kaengkaeh:\k*
\li2 Ef 6:14; 1 Pi 1:13
\p \k Kaengkaeh angzaeng:\k*
\li2 Ef 6:14
\p \k Kaengku hrang:\k*
\li2 Mt 3:4; 19:24; 23:24
\p \k Kahing:\k*
\li2 Mt 22:32; Jn 7:38; Ro 12:1; 6:11; Pi 2:4; Lp 7:17; 1:18; Lk 15:24; 1 Kr 15:22;
\p \k Kahnaem:\k*
\li2 Lk 1:48; 3:5
\p \k Kahni:\k*
\li2 Lp 7:14
\p \k Kahni im:\k*
\li2 Kahni im loe kai ohhaih ahmuen ah oh, to tih ai boeh loe kahni imthung ah kai ka oh, tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni. Praezaek ah Israel kaminawk ih Sithaw bokhaih im. Kawbaktih naah maw loe “amkhuenghaih im,” tiah doeh thuih o. Solomon mah tempul sah ai karoek to Isrealnawk loe hae kahni im thungah Sithaw to bok o (Tk 7:44-47). Long nuiah sak ih kahni im loe kaom tangtang van ih kahni im ih krang ah oh. Jesu duekhaih rang hoiah tangcaanawk loe van ih kahni im thungah akun o thai boeh (He 8-9). Jesu rang hoiah Sithaw loe anih tang kaminawk khaeah oh (Mt 1:18-23; Jn 1:14). Jesu loe Sithaw hoi angmah ih kaminawk salakah monghaih to sinh. Angmah tangcaanawk hoi nawnto oh lethaih om tih (Lp 21:3).
\p \k Kahoih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 12:31; Fi 1:10; He 1:4; Mt 19:17; Ro 7:18; 2 Kr 9:8; Ef 2:10; Fi 1:6; 2 Th 1:17; He 10:24
\p \k Kaipui:\k*
\li2 2 Ti 4:17; 1 Pi 5:8; Lp 5:5
\p \k Kakawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 7:13
\p \k Kalahta:\k*
\li2 1 Pi 2:9
\p \k Kalili:\k*
\li2 Palestine prae aluek bang ih ahmuen. Jesu loe Nazareth vangpui, Kalili prae ah qoeng tahang (Mt 4:12-25; Mk 1:9-28; Lk 4:14-19)
\p \k Kalingma thaih:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 4:2
\p \k Kami:\k*
\li2 Mt 4:4; Jn 3:3; Ro 6:6; 7:22; 1 Kr 11:8; Ef 4:24; Fi 2:8; Kol 3:10
