\p \k Kami capa:\k*
\li2 Jesu mah hae long nuiah toksak naah patoh ih ahmin. Cabu kangquem ah loe Sithaw kami thuih koehhaih ih ni. To kami loe dungzan kacak prae to hnu ueloe, kami boih mah anih to bok tih (Lp 1:12-18). Jesu loe angmah hoi angmah to Kami Capa, tiah thuih. Anih loe kami ah oh, toe Sithaw thacakhaih hoi sak thaihaih akaa to tawnh, tiah amtuengsak (Mt 26:64; Mk 2:1-12; Lk 9:26; Jn 3:13-15; 5:26-27; 12:20-36)
