\p \k Kri:\k*
\li2 Grik lok hoiah Jesu ih ahmin. Thuih koehhaih loe, Grik lok hoiah “moithawk nok, to tih ai boeh loe “qoih ih kami,” tih haih ih ni. Jesu duek pacoengah patoh ih ahmin ah oh. Kri loe duek pacoengah takpum ah amtueng e, taksa, to tih ai boeh loe ngan to om ai boeh, athii doeh om ai boeh, Pakhra hoi Muithla ah ni oh boeh. To Kri to Hebru lok hoiah “Messiah,” tiah kawk o. Jesu Kri loe angmah ih kaminawk khaeah pathlonghaih hnuksak hanah Sithaw mah qoih ih kami ah oh (Mt 16:13-20; Jn 1:40-42; Tk 3:17-26; 1 Jn 5:1)
\p \k Kri:\k*
\li2 Mt 2:4; 16:16; Jn 4:25; 11:27; Ro 5:6; 8:17; 1 Kr 2:2; 15:19; 2 Kr 5:17; Kl 2:20; Ef 2:10; Fi 1:21; 4:13; Kol 1:27; 1 Th 4:16; 1 Ti 1:15; He 13:8
\p \k Kricaabu:\k*
\li2 Kri tangcaanawk ih takpum. Tangcaanawk amkhuenghaih ahmuen. Jesu mah angmah ih takpum to bokhaih im, Kricaabu, tiah thuih. Taksa hoi athii kaom ai, Pakhra hoi Muithla ah kahing Kri ih takpum to Cabu kangtha thungah kricaabu, tiah kawk. Lokpaek Kangtha thungah loe kricaabunawk khaeah tarik ih ca to pop kue (Mt 18:15-20; Tk 11:19-26; Ro 12:3-8; 1 Kr 12:12-31; Kol 1:15-20)
\p \k Kricaabunawk:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 14:34; Lp 1:4
