\p \k Kri lok aek kami:\k*
\li2 Kri koeh ai kami, Kri ih lok aek kami. Hnukkhuem niah loe Kri ih lok aek kami, tiah kawk ih taqawk thacakhaih mah long to uk ueloe, kangsah cop Kri to angzo tih. Toe Kri tangtang angzo naah loe, angsah cop kri to Anih hum tih (2Th 2:1-12; Lp 11-13)
