\p \k Misong loihhaih poi:\k*
\li2 Judah kaminawk ih poih. Izip prae ah misong angtanghaih thung hoi kawbangmaw Sithaw mah pathlong, tito panoek poe han sak ih poih. Hae niah tuucaa to boh o moe, athii to thok ranui ah nok o. To naah Sithaw mah to im to caehtaak moe, imthung ah kaom angmah kaminawk ih hinghaih to pathlung pae. Jesu loe Sithaw ih Tuucaa ah oh. Kaminawk zaehaih thung hoi pathlong hanah angmah ih hinghaih to aicae hanah paek (Lk 22:7-16; 1 Kr 5:6-8)
