\p \k Mosi:\k*
\li2 Cabu kangquem ah Mosi loe Israelnawk zaehoikung kalen maeto ah oh. Cabu kangtha ah Mosi loe oeptang kaom zaehoikung, tiah tarik (Mt 17:1-13; Lk 24:44-49; He 3; He 11:23-29)
