\p \k Pathlonghaih:\k*
\li2 Zitthok, kasae thung hoi pathokhaih. Kaciim cabu thung ah tarik ih lokpui koek loe pathlonghaih hae ni. Cabu kangtha thung ah Jesu loe aicae pathlongkung ni, tiah amtueng. Anih khue mah ni aicae hae, hae long thung hoi pathlong thai tih (Mathai 1:18-21; Toksahkungnawk 16:16-34; 4:8-12; Rom 1:16-17; 10:9-13; 13:11; Efisa 2:1-10; 6:17; Luka 19:9; Johan 4:22; 2 Korinth 6:2; Filipi 2:12; Titu 2:11; Hebru 2:3; Lokphong 7:10; 12:10; 19:1)
