\p \k Patoeh ih kami:\k*
\li2 Jesu ih tamthanglok long pum ah thuih hanah Jesu mah qoih ih kaminawk. Jesu mah kami hathlai hnetto qoih. Jesu khaeah amtuk o pacoengah, nihcae to patoeh. Hnukkhuem ah Pawl hoi kalah kaminawk doeh patoeh ih kami ah oh o toeng (Mk 3:13-19; Tk 1:12-26; Ef 2:19-22)
