\p \k Pawl:\k*
\li2 Patoeh ih kami kalen hoi Jesu hnukbang kaminawk zaehoikung maeto ah oh. Pawl loe tangsuek naah Saul, tiah kawk o. Jesu anih khae amtueng pacoengah loe Pawl, tiah ahmin sak moe, Jesu hnukbang kami ah angcoeng (Tk 7:5-4; 8:3; 9:1-31). Pawl loe Gentelnawk khaeah tamthanglok hoih sinkung ah oh (Tk 13-28). Lokkam kanghta thungah Pawl mah tarik ih capat oh mangh (2Kr 12:1-10; Kl 1-2; Fi 1:12-30; 1 Th 1:1; 2:16; 1 Ti 1:12-17; 2 Pi 3:15-16)
