\p \k Piter:\k*
\li2 Jesu hnukbang hathlai hnetto thungah maeto ah oh. Anih loe patoeh ih kami ah doeh oh moe, Jerusalem kricaabu zaehoikung ah oh. Jesu mah anih ih ahmin to Simon hoiah Cepha (Grik hoi Piter,) tiah athlaeng pae (Mt 14:22-33; 16:13-20; Jn 1:35-42). Piter mah Jesu to ka panoek ai, tiah angphat taak (Lk 22:31-62; Jn 21). Hnukkhuem ah loe misahoih zaehoikung ah angcoeng moe, a tanghaih pongah thongim pakhrak o (Tk 1-4; Tk 9:32; 12:19; Kl 2:7-9)
