\li2 Mt 26:75; 3:3; Lk 6:21; 19:40-41; Jn 11:35; Ro 8:15; 12:15; Lp 21:4; 23:28
\p \k Qahhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 8:12; 25:30
\p \k Qaihma:\k*
\li2 Minawk boih taham lawkthuihaih hoi hmuenpaekhaih Sithaw khae tathlang kami ah oh. Israel prae ah loe qaima tok loe Levi acaeng thungah tapen kami khue mah ni sak thaih. Toe Lokkam kangtha thungah khet nahaeloe Jesu loe kasang koek qaima ah oh (He 4:14; 5:10; 10:19-25). Jesu hnukbang kaminawk loe qaima ah ni oh o (1 Pi 2:9-10)
\p \k Qaihma toksakhaih:\k*
\li2 1 Pi 2:5; 2:9
\p \k Qanh:\k*
\li2 Mt 13:44; Ja 4:13; 1 Kr 6:20; 2 Pi 2:1
\p \k Qawk:\k*
\li2 Amno ampa khae hoi hak ih qawk. Israelnawk loe loksuek ih baktih toengah Sithaw khae hoi kaciim prae to hnuk o. Kaciim cabu kangtha thungah Sithaw kaminawk loe Sithaw ih qawktoepkung ah oh o (Ro 8:15-17; 4:13; 8:17; Kl 3:26; 4:7; Titu 3:3-7; 1 Pi 5:3; 3:7; 1:4; Ef 3:6; 1:11; 5:5; He 11:7; Kol 3:24)
\p \k Qawktoep:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:5; 25:34; Mk 10:17; 1 Kr 6:9; He 6:12
\p \k Qoeng tahang:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 16:2
\p \k Qoih:\k*
\li2 Mt 20:16; 24:22; Lk 10:42; 18:7; Jn 15:16; Tk 9:15; 1 Kr 1:27; Ef 1:4; Ro 8:33; 2 Ti 2:10; 1 Pi 1:2
\p \k Qoihhaih:\k*
\li2 Ro 11:5; 2 Pi 1:10
\p \k Qoeng tahang:\k*
\li2 Ro 14:19; 1 Kr 8:1
\p \k Qoeng tahanghaih:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 14:12; Ef 4:12; Ro 15:2; 1 Kr 14:3
\p \k Qoeng tahang (Amprawk): \k*
\li2 Ef 2:21; 1 Pi 2:2; 2 Pi 3:18
\p \k Qong thai ai:\k*
\li2 1 Kr 9:25; 15:52; 1 Pi 1:4
\iot R
\p \k Raihaih:\k*
\li2 Jn 16:33; Ro 5:3; 12:12; 2 Kr 1:4; 7:4; Lp 7:14; Ro 5:3
\p \k Rang (loe): Ja 1:19 \k*
\p \k Rai parai:\k*
\li2 Mk 10:24; Tk 9:5; 2 Pi 3:16
\p \k Misatuh kaminawk ih angraeng:\k*
\li2 Misatuh kaminawk ih cumvaito ukkung Rom misatuh kaminawk ih angraeng (Mk 15:39; Lk 7:1-10)
\p \k Ruicinawk:\k*
\li2 1 Ti 4:7; Titu 1:14
\iot S
\p \k Saam:\k*
\li2 Laa, tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni. Sithaw pakoeh hanah kaminawk nawnto amkhueng o moe, laasak o (Kol 3:16; Ef 5:19; Ja 5: 13)
\p \k Sam:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:36; 10:30
\p \k Sabbath:\k*
\li2 Toksakhaih thung hoi Sithaw anghakhaih ni. Cabu kangquem thungah Sithaw mah angmah ih kaminawk khaeah Sabbath ni zah hanah thuih pae. Toe Jesu loe Sabbath kawng pongah Judah zaehoikungnawk hoi lok angaek o. Nihcae loe Sabbath niah toksak han ai ah, angmacae khosakhaih atawk to bokhaih bang ih daan thungah khrumh o (Mk 2:23; 3:6; Jn 5:1-15). Sabbath loe Jesu mah toksakhaih rang hoiah anghakhaih hoi monghaih hnuksakhaih ih ni. Kangzo hankoi hmuennawk ih krang ah ni oh (Jn 5:16-17; Kol 2:16-17; He 4:1-11)
\p \k Sadusi:\k*
\li2 Jesu dungah bokhaih bang zaehoikung abu maeto ih ahmin. Pop koek Sadusinawk loe bokhaih zaehoikung qaima tok to sak o moe, cabu kangquem kaalok khue pazui kami ah oh o. Farasinawk mah tarik thap ih daan to tapom o ai. Nihcae loe duek pacoengah kaom angthawk lethaih kawng to tang o ai. Farasinawk baktih toengah nihcae doeh Jesu hoi lok angaek o tuek tuek (Mt 16:1-12; Mk 12:18-27; Tk 5:12-42)
\p \k Sahkung:\k*
\li2 He 11:10
\p \k Saiqat:\k*
\li2 Lk 16:15; Fi 2:3
\p \k Sak:\k*
\li2 Jn 14:2; 1:3; Mt 5:27; 2 Ti 1:12; 1:13; 1 Pi 4:19; Ef 2:10; Kol 1:16; Lp 4:11; Mt 7:24; Ef 2:20; 1 Pi 2:5; Kl 4:19; 4:4; Fi 2:6; Fi 2:7
\p \k Sak amtonghaih:\k*
\li2 Jn 17:24; Ro 15:20; Ef 2:20; 2 Ti 2:19; He 11:10
\p \k Sak coek:\k*
\li2 Mt 23:34; Lk 1:17; He 11:16; Lp 21:2
\p \k Sak ih hmuen:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 5:17; Kl 6:15; Kol 1:15
\p \k Sakpazae:\k*
\li2 Mt 22:29; 1 Ti 6:10; Ja 5:19; Mt 18:15; Lk 23:4; 17:3; Ef 2:1
