\li2 Ro 1:20; Kol 2:9
\p \k Sithaw panoek ai:\k*
\li2 Kl 3:8
\p \k Sithaw panoekhaih:\k*
\li2 1 Ti 2:2; 4:7; 2 Ti 3:5; Titu 1:1
\p \k Sithaw panoek hoiah:\k*
\li2 2 Kr 1:12; Titu 2:12
\p \k Sithaw prae:\k*
\li2 Sithaw ohhaih prae. Sithaw mah uk ih prae (Mt 13:1-52; Mk 1:14-34; Kol 1:9-14; Lp 11:15-18)
\p \k Sithaw sakthaihhaih:\k*
\li2 2 Ti 3:16
\p \k Sithaw Tuucaa:\k*
\li2 Jesu to Sithaw ih Tuucaa, tiah kawk.
\p \k Situi nok:\k*
\li2 Tknawk 4:27; 2 Kr 1:21; Ja 5:14
