\p \k Tahamset (tahmen thoh):\k*
\li2 Ro 7:24; Lp 3:17
\p \k Tahamhoihhaih:\k*
\li2 Sithaw mah kami han tahamhoih paekhaih. Sithaw mah kami khaeah hmuen maw, to tih ai boeh loe tangqum maw paekhaih (Ro 12:14-21; 1 Kr 4:12;10:16; Ef 1:3; Ja 3:10)
\p \k Tahamhoihaih paek:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:3; 5:9; 21:9; Mk 10:16; Lk 1:28; Jn 20:29; Tk 20:35; Ro 1:25; 12:14; Lp 14:13
\p \k Tahmaa:\k*
\li2 Kaminawk khaeah angmah ih tamthang tamli sin hanah Sithaw angmah qoih ih kami ah oh (2Pi 1:19-21; Tk 11:27-28; 1 Pi 1:10-12). Jesu loe long nuiah Tahmaa kalen baktih toengah angzoh (Mk 13; Jn 6:14; Mt 10:41; 13:57; Jn 7:40)
\p \k Tahmaanawk:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:17; 7:12; 22:40; Lk 16:29; Tk 10:43; Ro 1:2; 1 Kr 12:28; He 1:1; Lp 22:6
\p \k Tahmat (anghmatsak): \k*
\li2 Tk 3:19
\p \k Tahmen, prawt:\k*
\li2 Sakpazaehaih pongah danpaek ai. zaehaih tahmen. Aicae zaehaihnawk boih Sithaw mah ang tahmen pae. Jesu mah aicae danpaekhaih to phawh boih (Mt 18:15-35; Kol 3:12-14; 1 Jn 1:9)
\p \k Tahmen (panoek pae): \k*
\li2 Lk 14:18; Ro 1:20
\p \k Tahmenhaih:\k*
\li2 Tk 18:27; Ro 3:24; 5:20; 6:14; 9:15; 11:31; 2 Kr 6:1; 12:9; 4:1; Ef 2:5; Kol 1:6; He 4:16; Ja 4:6; 3:17; 5:11; 1 Pi 3:7-8; 5:5; 2 Pi 1:7; 3:18; 1 Kr 13:4; Lk 1:50; 15:20; Mt 15:32; Mk 1:41
\p \k Tahmen kaom:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:7; Lk 6:36
\p \k Tahmenhaih katawn:\k*
\li2 1 Pi 2:3
\p \k Takang thohhaih:\k*
\li2 Caaknaek khaahaih, prae boih ah caaknaek tawn ai ah ohhaih atue. Kho angzo ai moe, pazu tavaanawk pung naah takaang thoh thaih (Mk 13:8)
\p \k Tahmenhaih:\k*
\li2 Amlunghaih hoi tahmenhaih minawk khae patuekhaih (2Kr 12:7-10; Ef 1:1-10; 1 Ti 1:12-17; He 4:14-16)
\p \k Takaw:\k*
\li2 Mt 4:4; 6:11; 7:9; Mk 7:5; Lk 7:33; 24:35; Jn 6:35; Tk 2:42; 1 Kr 10:16; 11:26; 2 Th 3:12
\p \k Takhi:\k*
\li2 Lp 17:25; Mt 8:26; Lk 8:25; Jn 3:8; Ef 4:14
\p \k Takii:\k*
\li2 Mt 21:42; Tk 4:11; Ef 2:20; 1 Pi 2:6
\p \k Takhinghaih:\k*
\li2 Kami maeto duek ai khoek to thinglam nuiah takhing, to tih ai boeh loe thinglam nuiah qui hoi zaeng. Thinglam loe kami zae hum han ih ni patoh (Lk 22:66, 23:56; 1 Kr 1:18-25; Kl 2:20
\p \k Takhing:\k*
\li2 Mt 20:19; 27:31; Ro 6:6; 1 Kr 1:23; 2 Kr 13:4: Kl 2:20; He 6:6
\p \k Takhisae:\k*
\li2 Mk 4:37
