\li2 Mt 6:4; Ro 2:16
\p \k Tamthanglok hoih:\k*
\li2 Gospel; Tamthanglok hoih, tamthanglok hoih taphonghaih. Jesu duekhaih hoi angthawk lethaih tamthanglok (Mt 24:14; Ro 1:16-17; Kl 3:6-9; Kol 1:5; 1 Th 1:4-5; Mk 16:15; 2 Kr 4:3; 11:4; 4:1-6; Ef 1:13; Fi 1:5; 1 Pi 4:6)
