\li2 Mk 9:23; Jn 3:15; 3:36; 6:35; 11:26; Ro 1:16; 1 Kr 13:7; 1 Jn 5:1; Jn 17:8; Tk 13:48; 2 Ti 1:12
\p \k Tang:\k*
\li2 Mt 9:28; Mk 9:24; Jn 4:48; 6:69; 14:1; 20:31; Tk 8:37; 16:31; Ro 10:9; He 11:6; 1 Jn 3:23
\p \k Tanghaih:\k*
\li2 Tangcakhaih, oeptanghaih. Na oep ih hmuen loe oh tangtang, tiah tanghaih hoi na hnuk ai ih hmuen to oh tangtang, tiah panoekhaih ih ni. Jesu tanghaih loe Baibul mah thuih ih baktih toengah Jesu kawng to tanghaihih to ni (Mt 6:30; 8:10; 9:22; 15:28; 17:20; 21:21; Mk 4:40; Lk 7:50; 18:8; 22:32; Tk 15:9; Ro 1:17; 3:25; 4:20; 5:1; 10:8; 10:17; 3:21-26; 1 Kr 13:2; 13:13; 15:14; 2 Kr 5:7; Kl 1:23; 2:20; 3:11; 3:23; 5:22; Ef 2:8; 3:17; 6:16; Fi 2:17; 3:7-11; Kol 1:23; 1 Th 1:3; 3:10; 5:8; 2 Th 1:4; 1 Ti 3:9; 6:12; 2 Ti 1:5; 4:7; He 10:22; 11:1; 11:6; 12:2; Ja 1:3; 2:17; 2:22; 5:15; 2 Pi 1:5; Jd 1:3; 1 Jn 5:1-5
\p \k Tanghang:\k*
\li2 Jn 15:5; Ro 11:16
\p \k Tangka hnikung:\k*
\li2 Lk 18:11; 1 Kr 5:11
\p \k Tangka hnikhaih:\k*
\li2 Mt 23:25
\p \k Tangoeng, pasoih:\k*
\li2 Loksae thuihhaih, loksae pathak thuihhaih. Anih tanghaih tawn ai kaminawk han khue ni Sithaw mah tangoeng, to tih ai boeh loe kasae thuih (1Kr 4:12)
\p \k Tangoeng (pasoih):\k*
\li2 Mt 5:44; Ro 12:14
\p \k Tangphrung long:\k*
\li2 Jn 9:6
\p \k Tangqum:\k*
