\p \k Tangsak (tapomsak): Ro 8:38 \k*
\p \k Tangtang:\k*
\li2 Ro 14:20; Fi 4:8; Ja 1:27; 3:17
\p \k Tangzat dueh kami:\k*
\li2 Mt 19:12; Tk 8:27
\p \k Tangzat hin aah:\k*
\li2 Fi 3:5; Kol 2:11
\p \k Tangzat hin aahhaih:\k*
\li2 Nongpa tangyat hin boenghaih, nongpa tangyat hin aahhaih. Kasae vah ving boeh, tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni. Hae loe Sithaw hoi Israek kaminawk salakah sak ih lokkamhaih, to tih ai boeh loe palungdue angmathaih ah oh (Ro 2:29; Kol 2:9-13; Kl 5:6; Kol 2:11)
\p \k Tangzun:\k*
