\p \k Tempul:\k*
\li2 Sithaw bokhaih im. Sithaw mah Israel caanawk khaeah angmah pakoeh hanah bokhaih im sak han thuih pae. Tempul thung Sithaw na bok o naah nangcae salakah kai ka oh, tito angmah kaminawk khaeah amtuengsak (Mk 11:15-17). Cabu kangtha thungah loe pum-im hae sithaw bokhaih im na ai boeh ni. Sithaw kaminawk ih takpum loe Sithaw ih tempul ah ni oh o boeh. Sithaw ih Muithla nihcae thungah oh (1 Kr 3:16-17; 6:19; 2 Kr 6:16; Ef 2:19-22; Lp 21:22; Jn 2:19; Lp 11:19; 21:22)
