\p \k Toeng (toenghaih): \k*
\li2 Katoeng hmuen to sak. Ciimcai hmuen to sak. Sithaw khue ni ciimcai moe, toeng (Ro 10:1-3;1Jn 2:1). Sithaw loe toeng baktih toengah angmah ih kaminawk doeh toeng han koeh. Kaminawk loe toeng ai pongah Sithaw mah angmah ih Capa Jesu to aicae khaeah patoeh, to naah aicae loe a toenghaih to anih rang hoiah a tawn o tih (Rom 3:9-24; 4:1-8; 2 Kr 5:21; Fi 3:4-9). Jesu hnukbang kaminawk khaeah Kacai Muithla vaihi toksak pongah nihcae loe katoeng ah khosah o tih (Ro 8:1-11; Kl 5:16-26; Ef 4:17-24)
\p \k Toeng:\k*
\li2 Mt 11:19; 12:37; Ro 1:17; 2:13; 3:24; 8:33; Kl 2:16; 3:24; 3:11; Titu 3:7; Ja 2:21; Tk 7:52; Fi 4:8
\p \k Toeng ai:\k*
\li2 Mt 5:45; Lk 16:8; 18:6; 18:11; Tk 24:15; 1 Pi 3:18; Jn 7:18; Ro 6:13; 2 Kr 6:14; 2 Pi 2:15; 1 Jn 1:9
\p \k Toenghaih:\k*
\li2 Sithaw hmaa ah katoeng ah ohhaih. Jesu hnukbang kaminawk loe toenghaih hnuk o, tipongah tih nahaeloe Jesu loe nihcae han duek moe, angthawk let boeh (Lk 18:9-14; Ro 3:21-31; 4:25; Kl 2:15-16)
\p \k Toenghaih:\k*
