\p \k Tuinuemhaih:\k*
\li2 Tui hoi pasaeh, tui thungah nup. Kami zaehaih loe pasaeh boeh, tiah hnuksak koehhaih ih ni. Tuinuemhaih rang hoiah kami loe zaehaih thungah Jesu hoi nawnto duek moe, hinghaih kangtha thungah Jesu hoi nawnto angthawk, tiah thuih koehhaih ih ni (Tk 2:36-41; 13:24; Ro 6:1-14; 6:4; 1 Kr 12:13; Ef 4:4-6; Titu 3:5; Mt 20:22; Mk 1:4; Ef 4:5; 1 Pi 3:21)
