\p \k Zion:\k*
\li2 Jerusalem vangpui taeng ih mae hmin. Sithaw ih tempul loe Zion mae nuiah sak ah oh. Atue atue naah loe Zion, to tih ai boeh loe Zion canu, tiah patoh ih lok to oh. To loe Jerusalem vangpui hoi Sithaw kaminawk boih thuih koehhaih ih ni. Cabu kangtha thungah loe Zion Mae, tiah lok to patoh, to loe Jerusalem vangpui kangtha hoi hmabang kangzo hankoi long kangtha hoi van kangtha thuih koehhaih ih ni (He 12:22-24; Lp 14:1; 21:1-2)
\p \k Zit:\k*
\li2 Lk 12:4; Mt 10:28; 14:27; Lk 1:50; 12:32; Ro 8:15; 2 Kr 7:1; Fi 2:12; 2 Ti 1:7; 1 Jn 4:18
